<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>104</hymn_number>
<author>Bliss, Philip Paul (1838-1876)</author>
<title>Duba Dai Mai Fansarmu LW104</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Duba dai Mai Fansarmu
 Ɗauke da zunubanmu,
 Yana shan wahalarmu,
 Halleluya, Mai Cetonmu !

[V2]
 2) Raini, duka, nasa ne,
 Ba'a, kunya, giciye,
 Mutuwa rabonsa ne,
 Halleluya, Mai Cetonmu!

[V3]
 3) Ba ya yi zilama ba,
 Ba ya faɗi ƙarya ba,
 Ba ya yi alfarma ba,
 Halleluya, Mai Cetonmu!

[V4]
 4) Ba ya buɗe baki ba,
 Ba ya yi kashedi ba,
 Ba ya mai da zagi ba,
 Halleluya, Mai Cetonmu!

[V5]
 5) Ga shi bisa itace,
 &quot;Gafarta musu,&quot; ya ce,
 Duba ceto cikakke,
 Halleluya, Mai Cetonmu!</lyrics>
</song>